# Orchestrate: Change Apply Coordination

This artifact configures and drives an **orchestrator agent** that coordinates applying one or more Ito changes, enforcing gate order, parallelism, and remediation policy.

## Inputs

- **orchestrate.md**: `{{ orchestrate_md_path }}`
- **Workflow skill (by convention)**: `{{ workflow_skill_name }}`
- **Preset**: `{{ preset_name }}`
{% if recommended_skills -%}
- **Recommended skills**: {% for skill in recommended_skills %}`{{ skill }}`{% if not loop.last %}, {% endif %}{% endfor %}
{% endif %}

