{% for gate in gate_order %}- `{{ gate }}`
{% endfor %}

## How This Works

1. The orchestrator agent reads `orchestrate.md` front matter + MUST/PREFER sections.
2. The orchestrator agent loads the workflow skill (`{{ workflow_skill_name }}`) if present in the harness.
3. The orchestrator builds a run plan and dispatches workers by gate.
4. Run state is persisted under `.ito/.state/orchestrate/runs/<run-id>/`.

